(People-oriented Economic Development)

265
00:12:48,620 --> 00:12:49,700
The company has decided

266
00:12:50,020 --> 00:12:51,580
to appoint Comrade He Jiahuan

267
00:12:51,580 --> 00:12:54,220
(Promotion Notice)
as the Director of Foreign Business.

268
00:13:08,620 --> 00:13:10,820
(Director's Office)

269
00:13:10,820 --> 00:13:12,020
Congratulations, Director He.

270
00:13:12,020 --> 00:13:13,060
You deserve it.

271
00:13:13,060 --> 00:13:14,460
In the future, under your leadership,

272
00:13:14,460 --> 00:13:15,780
we will definitely make rapid progress.

273
00:13:15,860 --> 00:13:17,580
It's all thanks to your support
for my work.

274
00:13:17,620 --> 00:13:18,830
Let's work hard together in the future.

275
00:13:19,380 --> 00:13:20,500
Alright, Director He,

276
00:13:20,500 --> 00:13:21,580
I'll go to work now.

277
00:13:23,980 --> 00:13:24,820
Director He.

278
00:13:47,820 --> 00:13:49,500
Hongyu, me, your Fourth Sister,

279
00:13:50,750 --> 00:13:52,650
when will my husband
be able to drive a taxi?

