00:14:10,700 --> 00:14:12,020
I've already paid the deposit,

281
00:14:13,380 --> 00:14:14,780
and asked Hongyu for help.

282
00:14:15,020 --> 00:14:17,060
You have to wait in line to drive a taxi.

283
00:14:17,620 --> 00:14:18,700
It's quite profitable.

284
00:14:31,660 --> 00:14:33,020
Did you hear what I said?

285
00:14:35,460 --> 00:14:36,620
I deliver goods,

286
00:14:36,620 --> 00:14:37,620
not people.

287
00:14:40,660 --> 00:14:41,500
No.

288
00:14:42,260 --> 00:14:44,380
What's the difference
between goods and people?

289
00:14:46,020 --> 00:14:47,820
Just treat people as goods.

290
00:14:47,900 --> 00:14:49,120
It's like being in a convoy.

291
00:14:49,620 --> 00:14:51,900
Get off at the destination
and you make money.

292
00:14:52,860 --> 00:14:54,460
Where can you find such a good deal?

293
00:14:56,460 --> 00:14:57,660
I only serve goods,

294
00:14:57,900 --> 00:14:58,900
not people.

295
00:15:00,780 --> 00:15:01,860
You are the master,

296
00:15:03,500 --> 00:15:04,900
and you don't serve people.

297
00:15:05,780 --> 00:15:07,020
In today's society,

298
00:15:07,170 --> 00:15:09,220
who doesn't serve others?

299
00:15:11,290 --> 00:15:12,700
Do you think I am

300
00:15:12,700 --> 00:15:13,800
enjoying a carefree life outside?

301
00:15:15,020 --> 00:15:16,300
Do you think I'm the Director now

302
00:15:16,300 --> 00:15:17,260
and I can do anything I like?

303
00:15:17,620 --> 00:15:19,220
Back in the days when I was the Deputy,

304
00:15:19,620 --> 00:15:22,420
I deal with the Director
and the Manager internally,

305
00:15:22,700 --> 00:15:24,340
and externally, I deal with the clients.

306
00:15:24,820 --> 00:15:26,620
At home, I take care of the children,

307
00:15:26,620 --> 00:15:27,860
and you, too.

308
00:15:31,900 --> 00:15:32,780
Director He,

309
00:15:32,980 --> 00:15:34,820
it must be hard for you.

310
00:15:35,060 --> 00:15:36,180
Don't eat too much at night.

311
00:15:40,660 --> 00:15:41,980
You can't put a crown on a clown

312
00:15:42,180 --> 00:15:43,180
and expect a king.

313
00:15:46,460 --> 00:15:47,900
As a laid-off worker,

314
00:15:48,660 --> 00:15:50,420
this is all I can do now.

315
00:15:58,140 --> 00:16:00,740
(Handsome Siblings)

316
00:16:03,820 --> 00:16:06,020
In the future,
don't buy so much at one time.

317
00:16:06,460 --> 00:16:07,700
This isn't much.

318
00:16:09,060 --> 00:16:10,260
And you have to choose.

319
00:16:10,820 --> 00:16:12,180
You can't buy everything.

320
00:16:12,260 --> 00:16:13,580
I just began to do this,

321
00:16:13,620 --> 00:16:14,900
just considering it as paying tuition.

322
00:16:16,100 --> 00:16:17,020
I discovered that

323
00:16:17,180 --> 00:16:18,260
leafy vegetables can't be stored.

324
00:16:18,420 --> 00:16:19,380
They don't last.

325
00:16:19,660 --> 00:16:20,820
They must be sold soon.

326
00:16:20,820 --> 00:16:22,450
So, I have to make small profits
and quick turnover.

327
00:16:23,700 --> 00:16:24,540
How about this?

328
00:16:25,500 --> 00:16:26,860
Don't sell these anymore.

329
00:16:26,860 --> 00:16:28,120
You can sell Tofu.

330
00:16:28,130 --> 00:16:28,980
Look at those few shops.

331
00:16:28,980 --> 00:16:31,100
Their Tofu is selling well.

332
00:16:31,340 --> 00:16:33,020
They are from Bagong Mountain.

333
00:16:33,020 --> 00:16:34,380
Their Tofu skills are all ancestral.

334
00:16:34,660 --> 00:16:36,140
Each of them has a Tofu Workshop.

335
00:16:36,140 --> 00:16:37,100
How can I compete with them?

336
00:16:38,820 --> 00:16:39,660
Selling Eggs.

337
00:16:40,700 --> 00:16:43,260
Isn't Weiguo familiar with the people
at the Chicken Farm?

338
00:16:43,300 --> 00:16:46,260
Ask him to contact them
and secure some supplies.

339
00:16:47,740 --> 00:16:50,300
You can also get my eggs.

340
00:16:51,260 --> 00:16:52,860
How many do you have?

341
00:16:52,940 --> 00:16:54,420
They are not enough for you to eat.

342
00:16:55,220 --> 00:16:56,860
I'll ask Weiguo later.

343
00:16:58,580 --> 00:16:59,540
Have some eggs.

344
00:17:02,660 --> 00:17:03,500
Jiali,

345
00:17:03,580 --> 00:17:06,060
- Ms. Liu is here.
- Wow, you've started a business.

346
00:17:06,500 --> 00:17:07,340
I was laid off,

347
00:17:07,350 --> 00:17:08,420
just trying to make a living.

348
00:17:08,460 --> 00:17:10,620
Isn't Jianguo's wages not enough
to live on?

349
00:17:10,980 --> 00:17:12,420
We have a son to raise.

350
00:17:12,980 --> 00:17:14,700
Isn't your son joining the army?

351
00:17:14,720 --> 00:17:16,140
After discharge,
he'll get a guaranteed job.

352
00:17:16,140 --> 00:17:17,060
If I were you,

353
00:17:17,060 --> 00:17:17,900
I would simply

354
00:17:18,300 --> 00:17:19,140
retire.

355
00:17:20,090 --> 00:17:20,940
I'm not that old yet.

356
00:17:20,940 --> 00:17:22,220
I can still do some work.

357
00:17:22,620 --> 00:17:23,620
Lady,

358
00:17:23,620 --> 00:17:24,860
her eggs are good.

359
00:17:24,860 --> 00:17:25,980
Why, have you tried them?

360
00:17:25,980 --> 00:17:27,260
Of course. Listen,

361
00:17:27,260 --> 00:17:28,300
I'm a regular customer.

362
00:17:28,300 --> 00:17:29,140
Did you see that?

363
00:17:29,260 --> 00:17:30,300
Zaolin free-range eggs.

364
00:17:30,300 --> 00:17:31,220
They're nutritious.

365
00:17:31,540 --> 00:17:32,740
From Zaolin, right?

366
00:17:33,140 --> 00:17:34,100
Free-range ones.

367
00:17:34,260 --> 00:17:35,500
These eggs are quite clean.

368
00:17:35,500 --> 00:17:37,020
Well, you see, she is clean too.

369
00:17:37,340 --> 00:17:38,260
- Get some?
- Okay.

370
00:17:38,260 --> 00:17:39,260
Give me ten.

371
00:17:39,580 --> 00:17:40,420
Alright.

372
00:17:43,740 --> 00:17:44,940
Here you are, ten.

373
00:17:44,940 --> 00:17:45,780
- Okay.
- Two yuan.

374
00:17:46,060 --> 00:17:47,060
Come back if it's tasty.

375
00:17:47,300 --> 00:17:48,340
- Alright.
- Thank you.

376
00:17:48,820 --> 00:17:49,660
See you.

377
00:17:50,220 --> 00:17:51,820
Thank you for bringing me business.

378
00:17:51,820 --> 00:17:52,660
It's the least I could do.

379
00:17:52,940 --> 00:17:53,820
Give me twenty of them.

380
00:17:53,820 --> 00:17:54,660
Alright.

381
00:17:56,020 --> 00:17:57,420
- Take the money.
- No.

382
00:17:57,420 --> 00:17:58,230
Why not?

383
00:17:58,230 --> 00:17:59,260
You're running a small business.

384
00:17:59,260 --> 00:18:00,550
Just do as you should.
Don't be too polite.

385
00:18:00,550 --> 00:18:01,950
Listen, even your Mom's Eight Treasures Dish,

386
00:18:01,950 --> 00:18:03,060
I never take it for free.

387
00:18:03,700 --> 00:18:05,060
Isn't this our Jiali?

388
00:18:05,540 --> 00:18:07,340
Why are you standing on the street here?

389
00:18:09,460 --> 00:18:11,860
I'm learning from you.
You're experienced.

390
00:18:12,340 --> 00:18:14,700
Could you share some tips with me?

391
00:18:16,300 --> 00:18:17,540
Why be modest?

392
00:18:17,540 --> 00:18:19,700
What tips do I have, right?

393
00:18:19,700 --> 00:18:22,020
I just deal with things as they come.

394
00:18:23,980 --> 00:18:26,660
Ms. Liu, your son should be
coming back soon, right?

395
00:18:28,620 --> 00:18:30,300
Yes, soon, he'll be back soon.

396
00:18:30,340 --> 00:18:31,860
China's money is not enough to earn.

397
00:18:32,260 --> 00:18:33,540
He went to America to make money.

398
00:18:34,020 --> 00:18:34,860
Impressive.

399
00:18:36,380 --> 00:18:37,220
Come on, take this.

400
00:18:37,600 --> 00:18:39,160
Give this to Jiaxi
to supplement her nutrition.

401
00:18:41,180 --> 00:18:42,020
No need.

402
00:18:43,980 --> 00:18:44,820
Look.

403
00:18:45,020 --> 00:18:46,260
You're a real sister.

404
00:18:46,260 --> 00:18:47,300
You treat me differently.

405
00:18:47,620 --> 00:18:48,860
Alright, I'm leaving now.

406
00:18:50,780 --> 00:18:51,740
She's leaving like this?

407
00:18:52,020 --> 00:18:52,860
No.

408
00:18:53,980 --> 00:18:56,020
With her coming, you waste two days?

409
00:18:56,340 --> 00:18:57,940
As sisters, we don't count this.

410
00:18:58,540 --> 00:18:59,780
I really dislike people like that.

411
00:18:59,780 --> 00:19:01,780
How unashamed she is!

412
00:19:03,820 --> 00:19:05,060
See you, Ms. Liu.

413
00:19:05,100 --> 00:19:06,140
- See you.
- Okay.

414
00:19:23,060 --> 00:19:23,900
Jiali.

415
00:19:26,140 --> 00:19:27,460
When did you start doing this?

416
00:19:27,700 --> 00:19:28,780
I didn't even dare to recognize you.

417
00:19:29,900 --> 00:19:31,020
A few days ago.

418
00:19:36,460 --> 00:19:38,340
Selling vegetables, my old profession.

419
00:19:42,620 --> 00:19:43,460
Let me help you.

420
00:19:43,780 --> 00:19:44,620
Let's go.

421
00:19:57,100 --> 00:19:58,260
You should find something to do.

422
00:19:59,060 --> 00:20:01,260
But the key is, this is too tiring,

423
00:20:01,260 --> 00:20:02,260
and it wastes time.

424
00:20:03,100 --> 00:20:03,940
I'm used to it.

425
00:20:05,860 --> 00:20:06,900
I will establish a branch

426
00:20:07,420 --> 00:20:09,060
for my bakery at Longhu Hotel.

427
00:20:09,620 --> 00:20:10,660
I've found the venue.

428
00:20:10,940 --> 00:20:11,940
Now I just need a store manager.

429
00:20:12,300 --> 00:20:13,260
Why don't you come?

430
00:20:14,020 --> 00:20:15,140
You're joking.

431
00:20:15,340 --> 00:20:16,700
How could I possibly do it?

432
00:20:18,500 --> 00:20:19,900
Don't be so quick to refuse

433
00:20:20,300 --> 00:20:21,860
I'm trying to recruit talent.

434
00:20:22,740 --> 00:20:23,820
If you come to be

435
00:20:24,100 --> 00:20:25,540
the store manager for this branch,

436
00:20:25,860 --> 00:20:28,060
the performance will surely
surpass the main store.

437
00:20:30,300 --> 00:20:31,140
Let's say goodbye here.

438
00:20:32,420 --> 00:20:33,260
Alright.

439
00:20:35,260 --> 00:20:36,260
Think about it carefully.

440
00:20:40,860 --> 00:20:41,980
Did he really say that?

441
00:20:42,540 --> 00:20:43,380
What's wrong?

442
00:20:43,820 --> 00:20:46,060
Do you think he wouldn't say that

443
00:20:46,060 --> 00:20:48,540
or do you think I'm not talented?

444
00:20:49,180 --> 00:20:50,580
Of course, you are talented.

445
00:20:53,420 --> 00:20:54,620
So, what's your opinion?

446
00:20:56,210 --> 00:20:58,100
I have no opinion. It's up to you.

447
00:20:58,580 --> 00:20:59,740
Look.

448
00:21:00,580 --> 00:21:02,260
I knew you would get angry.

449
00:21:03,740 --> 00:21:04,780
I'm not angry,

450
00:21:05,180 --> 00:21:06,940
not even the slightest bit unhappy.

451
00:21:07,260 --> 00:21:08,740
If he really needs a person,

452
00:21:08,940 --> 00:21:09,980
and you really want to do it,

453
00:21:10,020 --> 00:21:11,380
I will fully support you.

454
00:21:12,620 --> 00:21:14,180
You're not jealous at all?

455
00:21:16,460 --> 00:21:17,820
How many years have passed?

456
00:21:18,150 --> 00:21:19,460
Am I still holding a grudge?

457
00:21:20,710 --> 00:21:22,580
It's because you have a big heart,

458
00:21:22,620 --> 00:21:24,860
but it doesn't mean
others won't hold grudges, either.

459
00:21:25,260 --> 00:21:26,100
Who?

460
00:21:26,380 --> 00:21:27,460
Qiufang.

461
00:21:28,580 --> 00:21:30,580
Weimin meant well,

462
00:21:30,660 --> 00:21:33,380
but I have to think about Qiufang.

463
00:21:34,260 --> 00:21:35,260
Besides,

464
00:21:35,580 --> 00:21:37,780
I'm not familiar with the work
at the bakery either.

465
00:21:38,020 --> 00:21:39,060
It'll be awkward

466
00:21:39,820 --> 00:21:40,660
if I get involved.

467
00:21:41,620 --> 00:21:43,260
I'd rather stick to my own

468
00:21:43,260 --> 00:21:44,460
small shabby stall.

469
00:21:45,220 --> 00:21:46,980
Although it's small and shabby

470
00:21:48,260 --> 00:21:49,380
and might not make money,

471
00:21:51,140 --> 00:21:53,020
at least I have the final say.

472
00:21:53,940 --> 00:21:54,980
That's true.

473
00:21:55,980 --> 00:21:56,860
Independent.

474
00:21:57,420 --> 00:21:58,380
Self-reliant.

475
00:22:01,340 --> 00:22:03,380
Even in poverty,
we must maintain dignity.

476
00:22:04,940 --> 00:22:07,180
I have some news to tell you.

477
00:22:07,540 --> 00:22:08,580
Is it good or bad?

478
00:22:09,540 --> 00:22:10,860
Is it that our son sent a letter?

479
00:22:10,980 --> 00:22:13,020
No, it has nothing to do with him.

480
00:22:14,660 --> 00:22:15,820
Well, it's not proper.

481
00:22:16,060 --> 00:22:17,340
It does have something to do with him.

482
00:22:18,180 --> 00:22:19,180
What is it?

483
00:22:19,860 --> 00:22:21,180
- Hurry up and tell me.
- Listen to me.

484
00:22:21,780 --> 00:22:22,620
My work unit

485
00:22:22,900 --> 00:22:24,060
is going to allocate houses.

486
00:22:24,060 --> 00:22:24,900
Really?

487
00:22:25,780 --> 00:22:26,980
If we return the old house,

488
00:22:26,980 --> 00:22:29,060
we can get a new one at Longhu.

489
00:22:30,580 --> 00:22:31,660
Do you have enough points?

490
00:22:31,980 --> 00:22:33,980
Just enough for a two-bedroom apartment.

491
00:22:34,340 --> 00:22:35,500
A two-bedroom apartment.

492
00:22:37,860 --> 00:22:38,780
Which floor?

493
00:22:40,180 --> 00:22:41,180
Which floor do you want?

494
00:22:42,460 --> 00:22:44,580
How many floors are there in total?

495
00:22:44,580 --> 00:22:45,460
Four floors.

496
00:22:46,060 --> 00:22:47,380
Anyway, let's not take the first floor.

497
00:22:48,340 --> 00:22:49,180
Alright.

498
00:22:49,740 --> 00:22:50,580
It's up to you.

499
00:22:51,780 --> 00:22:54,580
Once we get the keys,
we'll move in right away.

500
00:22:55,780 --> 00:22:56,620
Okay.

501
00:23:13,540 --> 00:23:14,380
Xiaoling.

502
00:23:15,780 --> 00:23:16,940
Hongyu?

503
00:23:20,540 --> 00:23:21,740
Where are you going?

504
00:23:22,340 --> 00:23:23,780
Anywhere, just drive.

505
00:23:27,380 --> 00:23:29,140
Were you arguing with Zhenmin?

506
00:23:30,090 --> 00:23:32,260
He and I are like chalk and cheese.

507
00:23:32,520 --> 00:23:33,780
We are not on the same wavelength at all.

508
00:23:33,980 --> 00:23:35,340
I can't continue like this.

509
00:23:38,420 --> 00:23:39,260
Let's go.

510
00:23:39,500 --> 00:23:40,340
Okay.

511
00:23:51,820 --> 00:23:52,660
Who is it?

512
00:23:53,540 --> 00:23:54,380
Coming.

513
00:23:56,380 --> 00:23:57,260
Zhenmin.

514
00:23:57,260 --> 00:23:58,100
Qiufang.

515
00:23:58,660 --> 00:24:00,060
Go play with your aunt.

516
00:24:01,660 --> 00:24:03,580
Zhenmin, what's wrong?

517
00:24:06,900 --> 00:24:08,380
Didn't Xiaoling come back with you?

518
00:24:08,380 --> 00:24:09,260
I don't know.

519
00:24:15,740 --> 00:24:16,580
Xiaofang,

520
00:24:17,780 --> 00:24:19,060
take your brother inside to play.

521
00:24:19,260 --> 00:24:20,100
Okay.

522
00:24:20,300 --> 00:24:21,180
- Come on, baby.
- Okay,

523
00:24:22,140 --> 00:24:23,460
let's go inside and play.

524
00:24:32,180 --> 00:24:33,220
You had a fight again.

525
00:24:34,780 --> 00:24:36,180
You're already the head of the family.

526
00:24:36,860 --> 00:24:38,020
Can you be a bit more magnanimous?

527
00:24:39,180 --> 00:24:40,620
Stop fighting at every turn.

528
00:24:41,980 --> 00:24:44,380
The point is you always run home
when you fight.

529
00:24:51,340 --> 00:24:52,180
Zhenmin,

530
00:24:52,220 --> 00:24:53,100
what happened?

531
00:24:53,100 --> 00:24:53,940
It's disappointing.

532
00:24:54,540 --> 00:24:55,860
Tell us if there is any problem

533
00:24:55,980 --> 00:24:57,340
and we'll solve it together.

534
00:25:00,140 --> 00:25:00,980
Liu Xiaoling…

535
00:25:01,940 --> 00:25:03,420
Liu Xiaoling is a murderer!

536
00:25:05,780 --> 00:25:06,620
What?

537
00:25:14,980 --> 00:25:15,980
Liu Xiaoling, I'm telling you,

538
00:25:15,980 --> 00:25:17,940
you made a wrong decision.

539
00:25:18,180 --> 00:25:19,020
It's such a big matter,

540
00:25:19,020 --> 00:25:20,780
how could you decide on your own?

541
00:25:23,540 --> 00:25:24,780
I had no choice.

542
00:25:25,260 --> 00:25:26,500
The doctor said if I didn't operate,

543
00:25:26,500 --> 00:25:27,740
it would be very dangerous.

544
00:25:29,820 --> 00:25:30,660
Nonsense.

545
00:25:32,180 --> 00:25:33,860
You're just making excuses for yourself.

546
00:25:35,620 --> 00:25:36,580
You're the child's mom,

547
00:25:36,580 --> 00:25:37,740
Zhenmin's its dad,

548
00:25:38,060 --> 00:25:39,380
he has the right to know.

549
00:25:39,540 --> 00:25:41,380
I called him, but he didn't go with me.

550
00:25:43,780 --> 00:25:44,620
Tang Zhenmin,

551
00:25:44,980 --> 00:25:45,940
I'll ask you one last time.

552
00:25:45,940 --> 00:25:47,120
Are you going to the hospital with me?

553
00:25:47,460 --> 00:25:48,860
Are you sick?

554
00:25:48,860 --> 00:25:50,980
No, but I need to go to the hospital.

555
00:25:51,060 --> 00:25:52,980
If you're not sick,
why are you going to the hospital?

556
00:25:52,980 --> 00:25:53,820
Are you going or not?

557
00:25:53,890 --> 00:25:54,730
No.

558
00:26:03,620 --> 00:26:04,460
Nonsense.

559
00:26:17,660 --> 00:26:20,220
He doesn't have any
sense of responsibility at all.

560
00:26:20,380 --> 00:26:21,660
He has no energy at work,

561
00:26:21,660 --> 00:26:23,180
neither after work.

562
00:26:23,260 --> 00:26:24,620
