887
00:42:20,420 --> 00:42:21,980
Don't bother knowing it.

888
00:42:22,340 --> 00:42:23,740
Just distribute it to everyone.

889
00:42:24,340 --> 00:42:26,260
Everyone, finish the work well.

890
00:42:26,260 --> 00:42:27,100
Alright.

891
00:42:27,180 --> 00:42:28,020
Okay.

892
00:42:28,380 --> 00:42:29,380
I'm leaving now.

893
00:42:29,540 --> 00:42:30,380
Okay.

894
